original_title: Wills and Kate: The Road to Royal Romance
overview: With the promise of fame, fortune and a fairytale wedding, there was no shortage of women literally queuing up to take the hand of this tall and handsome Prince. But in 2002, to the sound of a million hearts breaking, William took himself off the market when he embarked on a romantic affair with Kate Middleton.
title: Wills and Kate: The Road to Royal Romance
